model.gizmos

Class Gizmo

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.gizmos.Gizmo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IGizmo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Absorber, Circle, Flipper, Square, Triangle

    public abstract class Gizmo
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGizmo
    A gizmo This abstract class provided the base for all of the gizmo's that the model has.

    • Method Detail

      • action

        protected void action()
        Performs the action of the gizmo This is called by the update method and should be overridden by individual gizmos. By default this does nothing, so it should be overridden to make things more interesting This action is interested in the triggeredPercentage value.
